<plot>This made-for-video documentary treats independent film fans to a behind-the-scenes look at the making of The Ugly One, Patrick Moug's directorial debut action film set on the streets of Detroit. Features interviews with the cast and crew of the film who share their experiences from working on the project, as well as discuss the special efforts that went into creating the finished product.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?063913</url></doc>
